ngthened.</p><p><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-296" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/logo-tunisie-2013_uk_r-300x160.png" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" srcset="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/logo-tunisie-2013_uk_r-300x160.png 300w, http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/logo-tunisie-2013_uk_r.png 425w" alt="" width="300" height="160" /></p><h2>Life inEgypt</h2><p>Despite having lived in and visited Egypt, I did not know much of what Egypt has to offer. Gaining acceptance to AUC triggered a process of discovering what I hitherto considered familiar. Underneath the political turmoil and economic instability is a thriving and diverse population that calls for unity and prosperity. I am still uncovering the secrets of Egypt. Who knows what I will discover?</p><p></p><p></p><p>To Education</p>";s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";s:11:"panels_info";a:7:{s:5:"class";s:31:"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget";s:3:"raw";b:0;s:4:"grid";i:0;s:4:"cell";i:0;s:2:"id";i:0;s:9:"widget_id";s:36:"fa770444-2210-466c-be93-279367b96c0b";s:5:"style";a:0:{}}}i:1;a:8:{s:4:"text";s:12:"To Education";s:3:"url";s:9:"post: 245";s:11:"button_icon";a:4:{s:13:"icon_selected";s:22:"fontawesome-university";s:10:"icon_color";s:7:"#000000";s:4:"icon";i:0;s:24:"so_field_container_state";s:4:"open";}s:6:"design";a:11:{s:5:"width";b:0;s:10:"width_unit";s:2:"px";s:5:"align";s:6:"center";s:5:"theme";s:4:"atom";s:12:"button_color";s:7:"#0099cc";s:10:"text_color";s:7:"#000000";s:5:"hover";b:1;s:9:"font_size";s:1:"1";s:8:"rounding";s:4:"0.25";s:7:"padding";s:1:"1";s:24:"so_field_container_state";s:6:"closed";}s:10:"attributes";a:5:{s:2:"id";s:0:"";s:7:"classes";s:0:"";s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:7:"onclick";s:0:"";s:24:"so_field_container_state";s:6:"closed";}s:12:"_sow_form_id";s:13:"587e35ec4ca3c";s:11:"panels_info";a:6:{s:5:"class";s:31:"SiteOrigin_Widget_Button_Widget";s:4:"grid";i:0;s:4:"cell";i:0;s:2:"id";i:1;s:9:"widget_id";s:36:"836d3c6c-d1