(1161, 257, '_panels_data_preview', 'a:3:{s:7:"widgets";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:6:"filter";s:1:"1";s:4:"text";s:1485:"<h2 style="color: #0099cc;" >Work experience</h2>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Digital Innovation: Consultant (intern).</li>\n 	<li>ESL teacher</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 style="color: #0099cc;" >Extracurricular activities:</h2>\n<ul>\n 	<li>American corner: assistant and member :</li>\n</ul>\nThe American Corner in Sousse is an independent English language library and cultural center geared for sharing information about the United States, foreign exchange program opportunities, improving language fluency and organizing activities and events.\nMy role in this organization included but was not limited to:\n*Hosting, organizing and advertising social events such as : monthly coffee house( Art talent show ), Guest speakers( community leaders, entrepreneurs, change makers, officials...), environmental acts( cleanups and campaigns )\n*Managing, founding and leading clubs: Media club, Drama club,book club...\n*Conducting workshops: programming, soft skill development, creative writing...\n*Welcoming guests and advertising the organization\n*General library work( supervising, book inventory, IT support...)\n<ul>\n 	<li>AUC Times: Writer</li>\n</ul>\nWrote 3 articles in the monthly main issues and 1 article in the special issue:\n\nRamadan Is Dead - We are the heroes of our time - All Hail President Trump - One Outlet, Two Revolutions\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Developers Club: Junior self-development trainer</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Nautical Club of Sousse: Licensed Rower</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<a class="ow-button-hover">\n\n\n</a>";s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";s:11:"panels_info";a:7:{s:5:"class";s:31:"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget";s:3:"raw";b:0;s:4:"grid";i:0;s:4:"cell";i:0;s:2:"id";i:0;s:9:"widget_id";s:36:"7966f7cb-26c6-40dc-9c5b-6da0009c3248";s:5:"style";a:0:{}}}i:1;a:8:{s:4:"text";s:29:"To Skills &amp; Achievements ";s:3:"url";s:9:"post: 259";s:11:"button_icon";a:4:{s:13:"